00:11:25.330 --> 00:11:28.930
At the time when Bach
was writing it, it was--

00:11:28.930 --> 00:11:33.260
we call this the "Well-Tempered
Clavier."

00:11:33.260 --> 00:11:35.680
Tuning is not the same as it was--

