00:46:09.560 --> 00:46:10.860
&gt;&gt; OK. OK.

00:46:10.860 --> 00:46:14.460
&gt;&gt; David Plylar: Yeah, which is
also a great piece, yeah, yeah.

00:46:14.460 --> 00:46:17.410
We can take one more
if there's one more.

00:46:17.410 --> 00:46:20.050
But there doesn't have
to be one more, does it?

00:46:20.050 --> 00:46:22.080
